    {
      "index": 2,
      "start": 29.574,
      "end": 32.356,
      "text": "I put too much on the line to wanna call it quits",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start": 32.377,
      "end": 35.0,
      "text": "That's why I bought you gifts, I really put my all in this",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start": 35.02,
      "end": 38.103,
      "text": "But you was too concerned with starting arguments and setbacks",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start": 38.503,
      "end": 40.746,
      "text": "Bringing up the past unwilling to accept facts",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start": 41.247,
      "end": 43.911,
      "text": "You dragged me into your world that's full of death traps",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start": 44.231,
      "end": 47.335,
      "text": "And had me hypnotised ignoring all the red flags",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start": 47.344,
      "end": 50.0,
      "text": "I fell for you trap and now I'm paying the price",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start": 50.401,
      "end": 52.905,
      "text": "I never would have thought you'd try to ruin my life",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start": 53.445,
      "end": 55.85,
      "text": "Should have known better when I looked in your eyes",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start": 55.951,
      "end": 58.795,
      "text": "Cause that pretty face is a massive disguise",
      "y_offset": 0,
      "words": []
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start": 60.018,
      "end": 62.923,
      "text": "So, so tired of the petty allegations",
